1) Cooking dinner

TURN ON stove top
HEAT frying pan
SPRAY olive oil
SET chicken on frying pan
WHILE chicken cooks
  SET rice in rice cooker
  WHEN water is evaporated
    TURN OFF rice cooker
  ENDIF
ENDWHILE
APPEND chicken to rice



2) Determing what to wear

IF weather < 70 degrees THEN
  WEAR jeans && hoodie
ELSIF weather > 85 degrees THEN
  WEAR shorts && tank top
ELSE
  WEAR sweatpants && t-shirt
ENDIF



3) Calculating a tip

DETERMINE pretax bill
MOVE decimal point one place to left
ROUND up to next easy number
DOUBLE new number
SET tip equal to new number